  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266980/extras/288555b1075944b11934d0a0cdb376bf.avif?t=1691604077\" width=612 height=64 /></span><br>Embark on a perilous journey through randomized sectors overrun by rogue AI-controlled drones in the aftermath of a catastrophic event. As a skilled Mercenary, your mission is to:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Uncover the origins of this devastating chaos<br></li><li>Hone your abilities and become ever more powerful</li></ul><br>Navigate treacherous landscapes, confront relentless adversaries, and forge your path to victory, growing stronger and more formidable with every daring attempt under the supervision of your commanding officer Ren.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266980/extras/20bda021bdd940615902906112da8106.poster.avif?t=1691604077\" width=580 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266980/extras/20bda021bdd940615902906112da8106.webm?t=1691604077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266980/extras/a8ed655d3811fca68a485d039b7ab328.avif?t=1691604077\" width=612 height=64 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unlock a wide range of formidable weapons and unleash your full potential in combat.<br></li><li>Harness the protective capabilities of energy shields, boosters, and other utility attachments to enhance your survivability.<br></li><li>Repurpose hostile drones and turn them into valuable allies to aid you in your mission.<br></li><li>Mix And Match powerful augmentations to amplify your destructive capabilities and dominate your enemies.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266980/extras/a49f0be046903c941dd60e09e723ea94.poster.avif?t=1691604077\" width=580 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266980/extras/a49f0be046903c941dd60e09e723ea94.webm?t=1691604077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266980/extras/ce3d56d3848f94572d0bac26f87528bc.avif?t=1691604077\" width=612 height=64 /></span><br>Your choices hold immense significance as you venture through a vast universe. Every decision shapes your path, leading to consequences that can be both transformative and impactful. Navigate wisely, for your choices will determine your destiny.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266980/extras/55e1f8516308ad762c25a5b455b197d0.poster.avif?t=1691604077\" width=580 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266980/extras/55e1f8516308ad762c25a5b455b197d0.webm?t=1691604077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266980/extras/b763fd01c7a7d69fce3eb0bc9404faf5.avif?t=1691604077\" width=612 height=64 /></span><br>As if one player was not bad enough, a friend can hop in and join the struggle.(persuasion skills are not included).",
